    "hero_title": "ABOUT THE EVENT",
    "hero_subtitle": "CERBERUS K9 2026 · 13–14 JUNE · OSTRÓW WIELKOPOLSKI",
    "section_title": "WHAT IS CERBERUS K9?",
    "body_p1": "CERBERUS K9 is Poland's largest and one of the region's biggest free knowledge-exchange platforms for canine operations, public security and defence. The event brings together professional uniformed services and civilians, world-class instructors and Polish specialists, theory and intensive practice.",
    "body_p2": "In 2025 we gathered over 150 participants from 7 countries — police, military, fire services, pro-defence organisations and civilian dog handlers. In 2026 we step up to the European level: confirmed attendance of US Police K9 SWAT, Portuguese Navy and 15+ NATO delegations."
